Package: touchpad-indicator
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
	gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
	gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0,
	gir1.2-appindicator3-0.1,
	gir1.2-notify-0.7,
	gir1.2-gio-2.0,
	gir1.2-rsvg-2.0,
	python3-xlib,
	python3-pyudev,
	python3-dbus,
	python3-evdev,
	xinput
Description: An indicator for the touchpad
 With touchpad-indicator you can enable or disable the touchpad, with shortcuts
 or by clicking on menu. Besides, it enables or disables the touchpad, when
 the computer returns from hibernation.
Recommends: xserver-xorg-input-synaptics | xserver-xorg-input-libinput
